        public static void resetHerdsAndAnimals(java.lang.String username,
                                        int popID,
                                        boolean deleteFilterCulling)
        Erase from temporal and/or persistent database, all animals and herds of the active population of an instructor
        Parameters:
        username - : Instructor's username
        popID - : Identifier of the active population
        deleteFilterCulling - : true means that all column filters are removed. False means that all filters are removed but a copy of them is saved at the culling herd.
